content: It's a good app. I just rather rankings than a fantasy price check.
The trade analyzer and price checker tools don't load most of the time, there are bad performance issues with the app.
Don't believe the hate. I use this loyally. Works great. No issues. Lot of people slam this app because they don't like the guy that created it. Even if he's a jerk, the app is a+++ @VoiceEnFuego
Dynasty game changer üëç
Half the time I try using the trade analyzer it times out, super frustrating for a paid app
Was really hoping this came with the dynasty guide as well.
It stopped loading players is there anyone who could help Ive bought it and superclex passes
Bought and paid for app,, twice. Wont load players and in the off chance it does, just says analyzing whenever i try anything...

I paid money to buy this app. Then they released changes to it forcing me to pay more for it to continue to be useful. So basically its a scam. Now I have an app that I paid for... which I can now longer use in the same manner that I could at time of purchase. Rip off.

This app is INSANELY priced!! It's not enough that it costs $5. But if you want access to the rookie class, it will cost an additional $5. If you play in a lot of professional dynasty leagues as I do you would need to unlock all levels. 2QB is an additional $5, and TE premium is $3. All in all, this app will end up costing $18 which is a great big RIP OFF!! Shame on you!!
Don't like the lack of transparency about what's unlocked to start. Do the rookies eventually unlock for free?

I like the values on players, but the season starts in just over a week and rookie values are still locked behind an additional $5 paywall. The price for this app is extremely deceptive, and that's the reasoning for my low rating.
Values do not change when change size of league. A qb in 8 man league should not have same value as 20 man league. Kinda a joke for the cost.
It's a great app after you pay for all the additional $5 for each settings like SuperFlex and Rookie rankings. Kinda greedy for features you expect to be included

Exceptional app for grading lifetime value of players within Dynasty. It's an absolute game changer in ensuring your getting the best deal possible. I was never a believer in these tools either until I used this one
Either the data is really out of date or they're incomplete but rookies are missing
Awesome work!
This dynasty apps, once purchased... does not include rookies. Again, a dynasty app that doesn't include rookies unless you pay double.

Good app. Works and looks good. Intuitive. The $5 app gets you most things but rookies. To access everything it's $18 by quick add. But that's worth it. Other calculators are about $15+ a year and web based / not as convenient

Great tool for startup drafts, been using it to accrue assets and set up dynasty leagues for long competitive stretches. Also dig the podcast, it feels genuine and not like those talking heads. I do have a couple suggestions; Have the adp as something we can scroll through. My suggestion would be to replace the ticker at the bottom with 4 smaller menu buttons "SF ADP, 1QB adp, SF+Rookie ADP, 1QB+R ADP". I ran out of space for the other one. @Optimal_Hunter if you want to hear it I guess??
freakin sweet, a trade tool by someone I trust. The update is super handy
Downloaded the app... It is 5.49 euro for it. Then if you want SF it is 5.49 more. 5.49 more for TE Premium and 5.49 more for rookies!! No thanks.

New update is sick! Google Play took 3 weeks to approve, so that's something to monitor, but the QoL improvements here are A+. This competes with any app of it's kind and then some. No one has a dynasty calculator like this.
The Dynasty Dominator is my go-to tool for player value and fantasy trade analysis. Appreciate you Podfather!

By far the most important tool for a Dynasty football player. With the player comparison tool on it as well for redraft leagues! Well worth the money!!! BUY THIS APP!!!!!!!! you won't be disappointed. Every additional feature offered after purchase well worth the money as well.
Best trade calculator app, bar none. Great user experience, great interface. Taking roster space into account in trades is a big edge. Love it
Only improvement would be Podfather life hacks tab.
Love the app, and very very useful for avid dynasty owners who love to trade or look for trades.
Always the best from rotounderworld
If you play dynasty, you will want this app.
Best Dyno app. Thnx Mansion!
i like it. lots of options. i use it with every trade because i like to win

Love the job you've down putting this together with limited resources. Use the app all the time for dynasty and while everything can use improvements this is pretty damn solid and better than most tools out there in my opinion.
The most Superior source of information for dynasty fantasy football there is. Hands down. On their own tier.
LOVE IT
Wonderful app! The additional cost for extra features is justified and worth it. Great for trades and quick lookups.
Incredibly useful app. The trade evaluator is THE industry standard. Well made and very easy to use. Best dynasty app available.
Great app, even before the update. ;)

So worth the money! The Trade Calculator alone has helped me ensure I wind up on the winning end of any and every deal I make now. The Price Check feature is one I use a lot to see who is rising and who is falling in the high stakes leagues. I use this and the Breakout Finder app all the time and can't wait for the season to start so I can stomp all my leaguemates!

Ive seen the one and two reviews and let me say please stop it. These guys produce the best dynasty content and show in the business. Also, all other "dynasty apps" are complete trash and are not apps at all. Do your research, use the tools and data and find out for yourself.
Going to start my 2nd season with DDominator App. I've crushed all the deals I've done so far. If it only had that feature, it would still be cheap. Matt Kelly is a dick but he knows his stuff.
My biggest issue with the app is that GOOGLE HASN'T ALLOWED THE FKN UPDATE!

This app is essential if you want to start making sense of dynasty football. If you pair this app with listening to Matt Kelley and Nate Lissanski on the RotoUnderworld Bobcast, you will find success, fun and domination within dynasty league football.
They put a lot of effort into the app and the content is top notch.
Love this app. Get to know your favorite players better
Great value calculator

I use this app for all my trades. I am in more than 40 dynasty leagues and use this app for all my trades valuation. I use it to break ties, determine if my valuations are on point. There is no doubt, this is by far the best dynasty app, and best tool. I have won numerous trades and this app has helped my teams. Love it for rookies and draft pick valuations. It's an absolute must. I am happy to support this team and will be a lifetime customer.
Such a good dynasty tool. $5 is amazingly fair, if not down right cheap. Best dynasty trade app, player profiles, compare players and prospects in both dynasty and seasonal.

App is so good. I use this tool constantly. So cheap for the amount you get out of it. Stop being cheap, $5 updates are nothing compared to it helping win your league year after year after year after.....

Great app! Player comparison tool is clean and easy to use. Trade analyzer is an awesome tool that removes the guesswork using real analytics. Can't help but appreciate all the unseen details that goes into making the tools within the app possible. Would recommend for sure- you won't get anywhere near the amount of content for such a small investment.
Great app, best trade values on the market
I have the advantage now. I use dynasty trade calculator to see what the average dynasty player will think, and I use this app to create the advantage.

If you play fantasy football and don't use this app you are only hurting yourself. The trade calc alone should sell you but a player comp tool as well? Too good. Podfather knocked this one out of the park.

It looks so slick. I agree with almost all of the evaluations but I mostly use it as a "sanity check" while proposing or accepting trades. The lifetime value and player comparison tools are super useful as well. Great app.
Awesome app. I use it for every trade I make.
Took over my first dynasty team (orphan) and made some moves, going to be using this to help during the rookie draft.
Great app. Matt and Nate, keep up the great work!
Great tool for Dynasty
Great for the hardcore players
Great app, worth it! As is listening to the RotoUnderworld podcast
App is one of a kind. Sharp to look at and a slick interface.
Love it. One of a kind. If only Google Play would get their heads out their asses and approve the new update my life would be complete.
This is the BFG of Trade Calculators. Buzzards are week AF.
Fantastic app

I've been using this app for over a year and am extremely happy with it! Being able to accurately diagnose trades, comparisons, player values, all while being able to use different league settings makes this a no brainer. Get an edge, utilize this app!

I listen to an absurd amount of fantasy football podcasts, and my favorite host is the Podfather because he excels at producing high-quality, entertaining podcasts that deliver accurate fantasy football analysis; the Dynasty Dominator is another high quality product from RotoUnderworld. My dynasty strategies and player values often align with the Podfather's, so it's nice to have this app to quickly check lifetime player values and analyze trades.
Love the app and love the website
Awesome detailed information for the serious fantasy footballer
The app creators care about the product, read reviews, continually improve the information in the app and the UX.

Damn good app considering it was concocted by a handful of people and spearheaded by a maniacal lunatic who just happens to be quite sensible when it comes to Fantasy Football.. same guys have a wildly entertaining RotoUnderworld podcast (also Matt Kelley looks like a young Joe Pesci)
Great resource for dynasty trading and value checking.
Great app, all the nerdy stats you could ask for

Love the app. Understand that any time you are paying for a trade calculator you are paying for a select group of Fantasy Football analyst' belief on players and positional values. So when you buy dynasty dominator, you should also be buying into Rotounderworld's rankings and try to listen to the podcast so you understand how they value players. Otherwise, you're just a blind fantasy pig finding fantasy acorns because Matt Kelley is placing them right in front of you thanks to this app.
Best dynasty app in the game. Great visual tool to show fools who think James Glass Conner are worth a top 5 dynasty pick
Best dynasty app!!!!!! Never gonna get stiffed in a trade. Dynasty lifetime values are always updated and accurate. Highly recommend
Love the app! Works great
Best dynasty App on the market.
Only app needed to dominate your dynasty league. Sleek, beautiful and easy to use. Highly recommended!!! #morefantasymansionlifestylehacks
The app is just a flat out incredible value. It works flawlessly. The update is great. The cheap add ons are vital and worth it. It's fantastic. Don't hesitate. I use it every week.
It's a great app, just a complete scam to make you have to pay again for 2020 rookies. They should tell you this up front.
I hated on it at first but realized the potential you gotta play to play
Greatest app ever!!! Thank you to the best in the business and the rest of the crew that work so hard to make this a 10 star app!

Brilliant app for all fantasy football leagues. The player comparison and trade evaluators for helped me better appreciate player values. This product along with the breakout finder and roto underworld have changed the way I view drafting.
Ugh, bought this app and am now getting gouged for 2QB data and 2020 rookies??? REFUND.
The Podfather kills it again!
Have to pay for Rookies? WTH. $5 for the App and then another $5 for Rookie info and $5 for superflex rankings and $5 for TE premium. Seems a bit much.

I decided to give this a try knowing people in my leagues use it. Went to enter my first trade evaluation, 2020 rookies cost 6.49 to add. SFLEX/2QB option is 6.49 to add. Don't waste your money. For the value, subscribe to DLF and get access to all apps and paid content or try Dynasty Trade Calculator.
not enough options. in a 2 qb league and cant even put that in as an option. not very good...
2020 rookies are drafted and signed yet not on the app yet? Oh wait that's because you want me to buy your other app that has the rookies on it? That's rude.
great tool.
Fantastic app for Fantasy football puts all of the most accurate fantasy information available at the touch of a button.
Constantly charges you for additional features like having to upgrade for SF and now pay for rookies. Better calculators out there
It's a decent resource but you have to shell out another $5 for the next draft class which is ridiculous when I purchased the app in the off-season.
Additional purchase for superflex option. Another additional purchase for 2020 rookies. Keep adding dollars to personalize the settings to your league. Disappointing!
Amazing!
Use this app everyday, initially bought last year for the trade calculator, but love the player comparison, just spent $5 again this year for the 2020 rookie class and worth every penny. Thanks guys
Great content, excellent functionality, and well supported app. Any dynasty fantasy football enthusiast should use this to supplement any other tools they already use to help them win their leagues.

Fantastic app at an excellent price. The Podfather hit the nail on the head and has exceeded my personal expectations for this app. This thing should easily cost 3x what it costs. Guarantee great return on investment for active fantasy footballers out there.
Great app!
I love this app.
Matt Kelly is the best analyst out there and damn does he know his stuff!!!!!! Would have paid a lot more than I did for what the app provides!
Far and away the best trade evaluator on the market. The Podfather nails it.
Don't know what I would do without this app!
One of the best in the dynasty fantasy football game! He was given The Podfather moniker for a reason

The app charges $6.50, then another $6.50 if you want superflex, then another $6.50 if you want TE premium, then another $6.50 if you want the rookies imported. Nice app, but tries to hustle you endlessly

Great tool for dynasty fantasy football players backed by the metrics of player profiler. Unlike the newly released breakout finder app from the same brand, this app is actually a tool, not just a set of metrics packaged into app form. If you sub to player profiler, you know that you can find the value metrics used in this app on the website. You can compare the lifetime value of the players on the website for your trades, but this apps adds the info around pick & open roster value as well.
Very nice, looking forward to see where this goes.

I appreciate the trade calculator. I wish it gave me a breakdown of the values, because in negotiations it helps to know individual values of each piece. You can do this with the price check, but have to leave the trade screen in order to do this. Also, my league has 7 rounds in our rookie draft. 6th and 7th round picks are not an option in the trade calc. Great app interface! With a few tweaks it could be the leading paywall trade calculator out there! In the running with DTC!
You have to pay AGAIN to access new rookie rankings... They are essentially asking you to pay for the app all over again every year. Would be nice to know up front.

This app has a nice simple interface and gets regular updates. Very handy. My chief complaint is that the Price Check section used to default to descending player value starting with the most valuable player. That got totally scrambled in the offseason and now that Price Check feature is not nearly as useful for getting an overview of player valuations. I hope this gets fixed ASAP as it cuts down functionality of the app. I wish we also got an update log to see when a player value was most recently adjusted.

Literally just bought the app and it's already asking to essentially pay the same figure again to access the 2020 rookies... absolute scam. The app is essentially out of date days after purchase unless you buy the thing again. Waste of money.
Must have for anyone in competitive Dynasty leagues or anyone looking for a larger edge in there casual league.
No explanation on price value chart and trade analyzer doesnt work. Id like a refund
Works great, good info
Doesn't even open up. Always closing itself.
Running the app on a Samsung Galaxy S10e. Sometimes the players won't load after multiple attempts. And a few times the app won't even open. Otherwise, it's a great app when it works.
I've downloaded the app twice and it would not open
Constantly crashing
The Podfather's frequently updated player lifetime values are an invaluable resource to any dynasty leaguer.
Best way to dominate the uninformed masses. I use it with all my dynasty trades.
Good app, pretty accurate values of players. But there are times I load the app and the player list won't populate, thus making it useless until the players decide to load up
I love the features but player profiler should be integrated in the app instead of being redirected to the browser. That would be a much smoother experience
Calculaor is good, but without a way to look at a list of ADP or sort it to rank rookies only it doesnt work nearly as well as you'd expect for a paid app.
No way to set # of teams, SF, TE Premium, or IDP. Just useless without that...how is Baker Mayfield worth less than Curtis Samuel in a 2QB League?!?!
I would never tell anyone I know about this app.

Excellent app. The superflex option is a necessity. I know you will get all uppity that we (your customers) have asked for it, but deal with it. 5 star app with superflex. EDIT: 2 QB setting added. Rating raised to 5 star. Screw you for charging $5 for it, but I paid it because it was cheaper than a cup of coffee. You got us good, Podfather. I may have to delay my retirement plans.
love it,but whem are we getting super flex as a league option
App is terrible! 500 characters is not enough to explain. doesnt define ratings and how they are determined. no easy way to sort/find rookies, sort information, etc.

A truly amazing and fluent application that will just keep growing! The best fantasy football application in the market place. The best part about this app, is the fact that Matt Kelly himself is leading the charge. His passion for fantasy football and his community shines through the Dynasty Dominator app.

Great app. The trade calculator is the best I've seen and the player value and comparison is nice. Would like for there to be a way to see the ADP all at once rather than having to watch the scroll at the bottom. I'm excited for the Superflex edition and hopefully a way to see all player values in a list format. Overall though, great app and well worth the money
finally a way to help evaluate dynasty trades
Amazing app! Another masterstroke from the genius of Matt Kelley!

Really Great, be even better if you could convert draft picks to rookie dollars and add player contract price and cap limits, as in our league these variables impact the value of the trade, also need to add defensive players for completeness

The app is decent. Lacks a few features though that should be upcoming in future updates. Hopefully the creator doesn't charge extra for things like Superflex, but I"m not optimistic about that. If he doesn't charge an extra $5, this app goes to 5-star immediately upon the release of Superflex update.
been waiting for this style of football app forever!
Excellent value for the price and the quality of the app is everything you'd expect from RotoUnderworld.
Excellant app
Patreon here, excited to support THE premier fantasy football analyst in the market, looking forward to using this app and seeing it grow. üöÄ
$4.99 is a steal. dont overthink this one

Started listening to the show a few months back. Matt's a funny guy and has a big personality but he knows what he's talking about. This app reflects that knowledge and is a must own for anyone in a Dynasty League. You're already investing a lot of time into Dynasty, so you should also invest in the right technology to get you to that championship. This app is extremely helpful and I'm really happy with it.
All your wildest hopes and dreams come true with the Podfather.
$5 worth every penny and more.
This app is slick! The interface is gorgeous and it's backed up with solid rankings. Seriously a steal for 5 bucks
Easy to use and very useful

I am very impressed with the slick interface and invaluable functionality. The Price Check feature which delivers a Lifetime Value metric and also references Dynasty startup ADP for each player is truly fantastic.
great tool to have at your disposal for dynasty
Very easy to use and very sexy to look at combined with meaningful fantasy football application. Great value considering most trade calculators have a monthly subscription. No brainer purchase.

How is this only $5?! Almost feel guilty getting it at this price. This app is incredible. The innovation vs other trade calcs really comes through on the trade eval (background podcast was great on the exponential lifetime value scores to differentiate the elite players, give proper value to empty roster spots, and appropriate value to draft picks). The player comparison is a great tool (not to mention really nice interface). And all this in the first version with more to come (superflex!)
Like the app.Very easy to use.App extremely straight forward.Cant wait to see hiw it compares to the other well known app's.

That app is cool for a trade evaluator and player comparison but for a paid app I think it should include a little more. The adp ticker is nice. I just wish I could look at a list instead of waiting for the ticker. Overall, the app looks nice, and I agree with others the trade evaluator is accurate. A few more added features or a cheaper price would change my rating to a 5. A rankings list would be great. I think the price check list might be ranked by adp, but im not sure.

You can evaluate trades and check player value. There are also settings that allow you to change league size and choose ppr, 1/2 ppr, or standard league scoring to give a more accurate evaluation. With it being a dynasty trade evaluator, you can also add future rookie picks (up to 5 years) to your trades. The app is smoove and is well designed. I would like to see superflex or a 2 QB setting added in the future.
*boner sound effect*
Really impressed with the app. Dynasty trades can be a challenge. I feel I have a distinct advantage over my leaguemates now.

This app is awesome. Been waiting for this for quite some time and it has not disappointed. I love the Price Check feature (even has a vibration as the meter goes up adding to the experience of watching the value of your stud rise). The Trade Evaluator uses Podfather's top secret Player Lifetime Value so you know you're getting solid value for $5. I l'm also a subscriber of the Player Profiler All-In package so this complements those resources nicely. Hit me up for more feedback @chalkwhite101
Most comprehensive and user friendly dynasty app out there. Lifetime price check tool finally brings actual dynasty values to the table, unlike every other calc out there

Now I can run my own damn team! App has a slick, minimalist interface, loads quickly and spits results out just as fast. Price Checker is great way to look at trends. Dynasty ADP ticker is a nice touch.
this is what we've been waiting for
